     A*
     A          R SFL01                     SFL
     A*%%TS  SD  20240318  153002  I0777       REL-V7R4M0  5770-WDS
     A            S1LIN#         4A  O  5  2
     A            S1ACCT         5A  O  5  7
     A            S1NOHZ         8Y 0O  5 13EDTWRD('    /  /  ')
